    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold strictly in as-is condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic repairs to be roadworthy. The engine currently has a loud knock and the transmission is slipping badly, making it unreliable for daily use. Externally, there is extensive rust on the body panels and the paint is peeling, while the interior has multiple tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. This is a project car best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a parts donor, and it will likely need to be towed.",
      "price": 4500.0,
